k with canvas. So in order to start using rough.js I need somehow to make these two libraries…","fields":{"slug":"/20201012-how-to-use-konva-with-rough-js/"},"frontmatter":{"date":"12 October, 2020","title":"How to use Konva with Rough.js","featuredImage":null}}}]}},"pageContext":{"skip":0,"limit":10}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}